# CardRadio (Momentum) — Momentum guidance (IDE)

**CardRadio** is a **card** that acts as a **radio**: only **one** **`checked`** item per **`name`**. **Requires `cardTitle` and `name`**. Arrow key navigation within the **same group** is supported. Wrap the set in **`role="radiogroup"`** and an **`aria-label`**.

See also: [Card](./card.mdc), [CardCheckbox](./cardcheckbox.mdc), [Radio](./radio.mdc).

Browse the [Momentum Components catalog](https://momentum.design/en/components/) for naming; Storybook documents props and examples. Reference: [Storybook — CardRadio / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-cardradio--docs). Optional: [Example](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/story/components-card-cardradio--example).

---

## Import

Requires <ThemeProvider> and <IconProvider> ancestors. See setup.mdc.

```jsx
import { CardRadio, Text } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";
```

---

## What it is

- **`name`:** groups radios; must be **identical** for cards in the same choice set.  
- **`checked`:** which card is selected.  
- **`onChange`:** when selection moves to this card.  
- **No nested interactives** in slots.  
- Inherits the same **card** layout/variant API as other card components (see [Card](./card.mdc)).  
- Prefer **`disabled`** on the React wrapper when exposed; **`setDisabled`** exists on the underlying class in some builds.

**Use `CardCheckbox`** for multi-select; **use `CardRadio`** for **exactly one** option in the group.

---

## Key props

- **`name`** and **`cardTitle`** (required) · **`checked`**, **`onChange`**, **`disabled`**, plus card layout props

---

## Example

```jsx
import { CardRadio, Text } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";


<div role="main">
  <CardRadio
    name="radio-card"
    variant="border"
    orientation="vertical"
    cardTitle="Title"
    subtitle="Subtitle"
    imageSrc="https://picsum.photos/seed/momentum-cr/640/360"
    imageAlt="Decorative card image"
    iconName="placeholder-bold"
    titleTagName="span"
    subtitleTagName="span"
  >
    <Text slot="body" tagname="span">
      One option in a shared name group—drive checked from React state so only one is selected.
    </Text>
  </CardRadio>
</div>
```

---

## Checklist for IDE prototypes

- [ ] **`ThemeProvider`** + **`IconProvider`** when using **`iconName`**  
- [ ] **`name`** is stable and **shared** across the group  
- [ ] **Exactly one** **`checked`** at a time in UI state (controlled React state)  
- [ ] **`role="radiogroup"`** + label on the wrapper  
- [ ] **Multi select** = **`CardCheckbox`**, not **`CardRadio`**  

Cross-check [Storybook — CardRadio / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-cardradio--docs) and your installed package version.
